{"id": 1354, "genre": 1001, "title": "你有哪些新习惯是电影电视剧带给你的？", "description": "做不了男/女主角，跟他们吃点同款食物总可以吧。（题图来自：LAURA LIEDO）", "record_count": 3575, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161129112915naKdUEVS5rsp07BP.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-12-09T03:00:28Z", "options": [{"id": 142080, "content": "一个人，碗勺铿锵，哈哈，所以吃饭都要看点电视剧。一般还是综艺。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506529}, {"id": 142081, "content": "衣服搭配！职业选择", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183621}, {"id": 142593, "content": "早上到办公室先来杯咖啡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443292}, {"id": 142082, "content": "在自己散步的时候，会自动哼歌当背景音乐，想像秀发风中飞舞~", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855392}, {"id": 142083, "content": "吃薯片蘸酱", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 857304}, {"id": 142084, "content": "英语粗口…WTF WTH bloody hell啥的", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 142085, "content": "看吸血鬼日记，突然变得想吸血了。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 860410}, {"id": 142086, "content": "辣白菜炒面、火锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723145}, {"id": 142087, "content": "吃饭看剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849859}, {"id": 142344, "content": "带耳机?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863163}, {"id": 143625, "content": "看国产剧成功学会了不断快进", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865597}, {"id": 142090, "content": "吃饭的时候看综艺", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 856569}, {"id": 142091, "content": "指甲剪的短短的 手臂练的粗粗的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759780}, {"id": 142092, "content": "爱装逼喝